                        <div id="page-title">
                            中国分部异常项目
                        </div>
                    

                    

                    



                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<p><strong>前言：</strong>SCP基金会中国分部发现了为数不少的项目无用而不值得进一步关注。本文件列出了那些激起了一些好奇心的项目。如果这些项目的知识在将来变得有用或必要，则可以将其作为一种资源。<br />
— █████博士，Site-CN-██研究主管</p>
<p>欲查看已归档的异常项目记录，请<a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn-arc">点击这里</a>。</p>
<hr />
<div class="list-pages-box">    <div class="list-pages-item">


<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button create-button" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00520/parentPage/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/#_editpage">添加新的记录</a></p>
</div>
    
    
    
    </div>
<p style="text-align: center;">显示顺序：<a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/order/rating%20desc">评分较高</a> | <a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/order/rating">评分较低</a> | <a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/order/name">最早发布</a> | <a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/order/name%20desc">最新发布</a> | <a href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn/order/random">随机</a></p>
<p><strong>提示：</strong>如果你希望改变你的评分，请先点击“X”取消你的评分，再重新评分。</p>
<hr />
<div class="list-pages-box">    <div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00224/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一张铁架床，当有人躺在项目上并且闭上眼睛时，此人将持续听见“嗡嗡”声当对象睁眼时异常性质消失<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>Dr.pigeon的卧室中<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>放置于低价值异常物品收容室<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>哪里有蚊子啊啊啊啊！搞得我一宿没睡觉啊啊啊啊！</em>——在卧室中喷了一整瓶花露水的Dr.pigeon</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00224" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00224" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00224-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpionidaslaughter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6306406); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6306406&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180073" alt="ScorpionidaSlaughter" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6306406)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpionidaslaughter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6306406); return false;">ScorpionidaSlaughter</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1590860663 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">30 May 2020 17:44</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00223/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一桶盛有约250ml面汤的泡面，底部不可见。可以不断地从中捞出面渣与脱水蔬菜。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>位于Site-CN-██的生物实验室内。<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>一次测试中将面汤倒出后失去异常性质。后将面汤倒回并冷藏。<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>虽然因为违反实验室规定而扣了工资，但我没喝汤就吃饱这可是第一次。</em>——Dr.Kalis<br />
<em>然后为了检测同一批泡面是否异常，半个部门的人被鼓励着吃了三天泡面。</em>——Dr.Lujeff</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00223" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00223" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00223-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lujeff-kalis" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5460271); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5460271&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180073" alt="Lujeff Kalis" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5460271)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lujeff-kalis" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5460271); return false;">Lujeff Kalis</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1590758040 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">29 May 2020 13:14</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00222/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一张10m的裹尸布。当项目与一处于醉酒状态的人类个体处在一个单独的空间内时，项目将会瞬移至对象的身边，并完全包裹住对象的身体。期间对象能够正常呼吸但报告称感受到持续的“窒息感”。在异常效应显现十分钟后对象将会直接死亡，经鉴定死亡原因为窒息而死。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>████/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>████<br />
<strong>目前状态：</strong>Site-CN-75的标准异常物品收容柜内。</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00222" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00222" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00222-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yoghurt-rescuer" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3167340); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3167340&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180074" alt="Yoghurt-rescuer" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3167340)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yoghurt-rescuer" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3167340); return false;">Yoghurt-rescuer</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1590679306 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">28 May 2020 15:21</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00221/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一个████牌头戴式耳机，在被人用来听歌时，使用者会不自觉地唱出正在听的歌<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>Dr.pigeon的办公室<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>被放置于Site-██低价值异常物品收容室中<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>I want something just like this～Oh, I want something just like this～</em>——正在使用项目听歌的Dr.pigeon<br />
<em>Oh,I want something just he stop！</em>——被Dr.pigeon的歌声折磨到崩溃的特工fan</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00221" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00221" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00221-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpionidaslaughter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6306406); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6306406&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180074" alt="ScorpionidaSlaughter" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6306406)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/scorpionidaslaughter" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6306406); return false;">ScorpionidaSlaughter</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1590676061 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">28 May 2020 14:27</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00220/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一组基金会制斯克兰顿现实稳定锚（SRA）。其在直接视觉观察上与普通船锚无异。将其作为船锚使用时会使作用船只永久锚定于当前位置。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>Area-CN-██收容设施<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>被就地收容于Area-CN-██。<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong><em>这就是<a href="/scp-cn-1730">SCP-CN-1730</a>漂在海上还能完全不动的原因？</em>——Dir. ██████</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00220" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00220" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00220-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-hormress" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4142571); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4142571&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180074" alt="Dr Hormress" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4142571)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-hormress" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4142571); return false;">Dr Hormress</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1590666363 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">28 May 2020 11:46</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00218/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一个回形针，任何夹在里面的纸最终都会显现出0.3厘米的厚度，该项目理论上可以夹带无数张纸。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>Dr.阙的办公桌上。<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>收容于Dr.李的办公桌上。<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong>Dr.李跟我说这是个Keter级的收容物，而且我当时居然还信了！——Dr.阙</p>
