</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00194/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>項鉬媌述：</strong>壹(1)支嘿銫圓銖筆。鉂砽項鉬書瀉の傼茡，以忣媌述垓項鉬の傼茡嘟鱂桧被轉换爲煋芠。Letters except Chinese characters will not be affected.<br />
<strong>迴収ㄖ期：</strong>20██/██/██<br />
<strong>迴収地點：</strong>深zんeи鈰████汏㙾<br />
<strong>當椾狀態：</strong>被収容玗Site-CN-██低價ィ直粅ρiη収容匮。</p>
<div style="text-align: right;">
<p><span id="u-credit-00194" class="option-button fa fa-info-circle">信息</span><a class="option-button fa fa-edit" href="/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00194" target="_blank">编辑</a></p>
</div>
<div id="u-credit-00194-hovertip">
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/coldmist" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6439634); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6439634&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610180074" alt="Coldmist" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6439634)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/coldmist" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6439634); return false;">Coldmist</a></span></p>
<p><strong>发布日期：</strong><span class="odate time_1589353886 format_%25Y-%25m-%25d">13 May 2020 07:11</span></p>
</div>
<hr />
</div>
<div class="list-pages-item">


<p><iframe src="http://scp-wiki-cn.wikidot.com/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:00191/?theme_url=http://scp-wiki-cn.wdfiles.com/local--code/log-of-anomalous-items-cn:_theme/1" align="" frameborder="0" height="" scrolling="no" width="" class="" style="width:100%;height:26px;overflow:hidden"></iframe></p>
<p><strong>项目描述：</strong>一包████品牌的早餐面包，面包已经严重变质。在超过包装上注明的保质期后的1～2天内，生产日期将会自行向后变更一个月，袋中商品不受影响。<br />
<strong>回收日期：</strong>2020/01/██<br />
<strong>回收地点：</strong>浙江省杭州市██区一小卖部内<br />
<strong>当前状态：</strong>袋中面包经检测后已销毁。包装袋已进行消毒处理，现收容于Site-CN-03的低价值物品储藏柜中。<br />
<strong>笔记：</strong>我好像知道上次那包害我拉肚子的豆腐干是怎么一回事了。——艾特工<br />
不，我觉得那只是单纯的食品安全问题，或者是无良商家改了生产日期。——研究员洛██</p>
